com.here.android.mpa.streetlevel

Class StreetLevelIcon

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.common.ViewObject
      • com.here.android.mpa.streetlevel.StreetLevelObject
        • com.here.android.mpa.streetlevel.StreetLevelIconBase
          • com.here.android.mpa.streetlevel.StreetLevelIcon

  • public final class StreetLevelIcon
extends StreetLevelIconBase
    Represents a class for all street-level icon objects. Users can add a StreetLevelIcon object to an on-screen StreetLevelModel instance by binding it with a StreetLevelFragment object.
